    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It is in absolutely pristine condition and has been pampered since the very first day. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it\u2014honestly, there isn't a single scratch or dent to be found! It drives like an absolute dream and still has that wonderful new-car feel. I\u2019m genuinely sad to let it go, but I know it\u2019s going to make its next owner so happy. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
