      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a total dream ride? I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute gem of a car, and honestly, it\u2019s in incredible shape\u2014it looks and feels just like it rolled right off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered, kept tucked away in a garage, and the interior is still totally spotless. You really won't find another one this clean. Seriously, it's a beauty! Swing by and take a look for yourself\u2014I promise you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 44900.0,
