    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD. This example retains its original 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine, exhibiting exceptional compression across all rotor faces. The chassis remains factory-spec with its lightweight aluminum double-wishbone suspension and Torsen limited-slip differential providing surgical turn-in and high-speed stability. Meticulously maintained with zero vacuum leaks in the complex sequential control system, the boost transition remains seamless and linear. Finished in pristine original paint with a flawless, wear-free interior, this is a turnkey, collector-quality specimen showcasing the pinnacle of 90s Japanese performance engineering.",
